Interface OmemoMessageListener


  • public interface OmemoMessageListener
    Listener interface that allows implementations to receive decrypted OMEMO messages.

    • Method Detail

      • onOmemoMessageReceived

        void onOmemoMessageReceived(String decryptedBody,
                            Message encryptedMessage,
                            Message wrappingMessage,
                            OmemoMessageInformation omemoInformation)
        Gets called, whenever an OmemoMessage has been received and was successfully decrypted.
        Parameters:
        decryptedBody - Decrypted body
        encryptedMessage - Encrypted Message
        wrappingMessage - Wrapping carbon message, in case the message was a carbon copy, else null.
        omemoInformation - Information about the messages encryption etc.

      • onOmemoKeyTransportReceived

        void onOmemoKeyTransportReceived(CipherAndAuthTag cipherAndAuthTag,
                                 Message message,
                                 Message wrappingMessage,
                                 OmemoMessageInformation omemoInformation)
        Gets called, whenever an OmemoElement without a body (an OmemoKeyTransportElement) is received.
        Parameters:
        cipherAndAuthTag - transported Cipher along with an optional AuthTag
        message - Message that contained the KeyTransport
        wrappingMessage - Wrapping message (eg. carbon), or null
        omemoInformation - Information about the messages encryption etc.
